Because that's the condition for the possibility now of Jesus from the height of this higher dimension.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.840
Now commanding.

00:06:43.776 --> 00:06:45.440
The work of his church

00:06:46.208 --> 00:06:48.800
It's why we speak of his

00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:56.448
obsession or his being seated at the right hand of the Father? Well, in the ancient world, the seat of

