Jesus is being envisioned here as a kind of

00:07:12.224 --> 00:07:14.880
Plenipotentiary of the father

00:07:14.688 --> 00:07:19.136
The one who is ruling with the full authority of the Father.

00:07:19.232 --> 00:07:29.280
Yeah. Don't see this in a subordinacious way as though Jesus is someone less than the Father. No, no. He's at the right hand of the Father with the planopotentia, the full power.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:31.616
power of the Father. And now is 100% true.

00:07:31.872 --> 00:07:34.592
Directing operations.

00:07:34.880 --> 00:07:42.080
That's Jesus now in relation to the totality of the church. Now, to anticipate next week, Jesus.

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:47.904
What are he and the Father going to do from their exalted place, but send out

00:07:47.968 --> 00:07:50.016
The Holy Spirit

00:07:50.176 --> 00:07:55.008
To enable and equip his apostles to do his work in the world.

00:07:55.648 --> 00:07:59.264
Yes. That's the political, if you want, dimension of the ascension, right?

00:07:59.424 --> 00:08:01.600
Christ the Lord.

00:08:01.568 --> 00:08:04.480
So when Paul keeps saying, "Jesus, carry us."

00:08:04.832 --> 00:08:06.688
As a challenge, of course,

00:08:06.816 --> 00:08:12.672
to the claim that Caesar was the Lord. No, no, Jesus is the true Lord who is the commander.

