The commander of all things, ordering his church according to his purposes.

00:08:17.792 --> 00:08:22.368
Okay, that's one dimension, a very important one, I think, of the ascension, right?

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:26.528
The second one I'm going to call liturgical.

00:08:26.752 --> 00:08:29.344
liturgical and I want to refer to

00:08:29.472 --> 00:08:33.664
So our text for today for the Feast of the Ascension, taken from 1 John 3, verses 1-

