Now, this is a reference to Yom Kippur, the Day of Atonement, the highest of the High Holy Days.

00:10:37.056 --> 00:10:39.136
100%. When once a year, when once a year

00:10:38.816 --> 00:10:48.864
The high priest in the temple would enter into the holy of holies, and he'd slaughter an animal there. He would sprinkle the blood around, and then he'd come out through the veil.

00:10:48.384 --> 00:10:58.432
veil. Remember the veil that is torn at the crucifixion? He comes out through that veil and he sprinkles the people. It was the great moment of sacrifice whereby Israel

00:10:57.952 --> 00:11:00.416
Israel was reconciled to the Lord.

00:11:00.416 --> 00:11:05.280
We're the sins of the nation we're taking away and the mercy of God offer.

